Running query: When installing the robot on a non-ideal foundation, how do flatness, tilt, and resonance frequency affect robot accuracy and performance, and what corrective actions are recommended?

[SEARCH] Query: 'robot installation foundation flatness tilt resonance frequency accuracy performance corrective actions'
[SEARCH] Backend return type: coroutine
